item.title: Prayer bpn6211 in Hawaiian
item.description: ##He Pule Koi Pˆkole *Short Obligatory Prayer ˇO wau ko’u ho’ike, e ku’u Akua, nau i hana mai ia’u e ho’omaopopo ia ˇOe a’e ho’omana ia ˇOe. Ke ho’oia’i’o nei wau i kÎia manawa, i ko’u ikaika ˇole a me Kou mana ikaika, i ku’u ˇilihune a i Kou waiwai palena ˇole. ˇA’ole mea e a’e, ˇO ˇOe wale no e ku’u Akua, he Kokua kokoke i ka wa popilikia, ˇO ˇOe ka mea apau, nau i hana na mea apau.
